Synopsis: This is the all-American love story. Boy meets girl, boy and girl fall in love, and so on. But because this is distinctively pornographic rendering of the all-American love story starring some of the blue movie biz's hottest and most sought-after stars, there is also plenty of explicit sex at those points in mainstream movies where the camera discreetly cuts away. Nikki Tyler is the young woman in love here, and the stunning blonde bombshell is at the top of her game in both the acting and sexing categories. When Nikki's lover dies without a will, his evil niece Jeanna takes her place in his home, causing everyone to hate her in the process. But right before the will is read, the two vixens discover the one thing they may have in common: A lust for one another. And after they've stated their desire, they vow to take care of each other regardless of how the will reads. Join the spectacular Nikki Tyler in this first girl/girl starring role, along with a terrific Jenteal, and the smoldering Jeanna Fine in American Pie.
